GET Route
    used to retrieve information
    data is sent via query string
    information is plainly visible in the url
    limited amount of data can be sent

POST Route 
    used to post to the server
    used to write/create
    data is sent via request body
    any amount of data can be sent

REST 
    Representation State Transfer
    an architechtural style for distributing hypermedia systems
    a set of guidelines for how client and server communicates

